rows.label: qst201409_msg0001
rows.name: No one's coming past...

rows.label: qst201409_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, waiting around's no good. Let's go
and look for someone.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh! Hello, you two. Are you taking a
little constitutional?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0004
rows.name: ...Is that what you're doing?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0005
rows.name: Why, yes!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0006
rows.name:
I always take a little stroll in the night
air, it aids sleep.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0007
rows.name: Huh? Really?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0008
rows.name: Kagutsuchi... We'd like to ask you a favor.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0009
rows.name:
Would you mind chatting with us for a
bit, and then telling us which one of us
has the most Girl Power?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0010
rows.name:
Oh! A thrilling contest, I'm sure!
Certainly, I'd be happy to join in!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0011
rows.name: Thank you!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0012
rows.name:
Well, since we have Kagutsuchi here,
should we talk about beauty?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0027
rows.name:
Yeah! That's a topic I'm pretty
confident on!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0013
rows.name:
My cleanse, tone and moisturize
routine takes some beating, I tell you.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0014
rows.name:
And I'm always practicing throwing
cute poses in front of the mirror.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0015
rows.name:
If I may say, that's a rather narrow
way to define beauty, Zakuro.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0016
rows.name:
...I'm not sure beauty is something
you practice. It's something you
radiate from within.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0017
rows.name:
I don't think I really need to go
to those lengths to look good.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0018
rows.name:
I always aim for new heights of beauty!
It's like, one of my life goals!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0019
rows.name:
Ever onward! Always pushing the
very boundaries of beauty!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0020
rows.name:
Certainly, it's good to set yourself
goals...

rows.label: qst201409_msg0021
rows.name:
A little healthy rivalry doesn't hurt
either.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0022
rows.name:
Of course, the rivalry should always
be handled graciously...

rows.label: qst201409_msg0023
rows.name: So, I'd say this one's a draw, girls.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0024
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0025
rows.name: What...?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0026
rows.name:
I think you both need to grow
spiritually a little before you can
really hold forth about beauty.
